the city as Mr. Proposal Fail.

14:05.971 --> 14:09.057
You know who liked the video
last week on Twitter? Michelle Obama.

14:10.434 --> 14:13.520
‐ How did you forget
the Beyoncé tickets at the bar?

14:13.520 --> 14:15.272
ALL:
Surprise!

14:15.981 --> 14:18.275
‐ What's happening?

14:18.275 --> 14:20.277
‐ Hannah...

14:21.778 --> 14:23.822
I remember the moment
I fell in love with you.

14:25.407 --> 14:27.743
