14:43.675 --> 14:44.968
This is the girl for me.

14:44.968 --> 14:46.637
Aww...

14:47.971 --> 14:50.390
Hannah, I believe we can make it
through anything together.

14:51.099 --> 14:54.645
Even if sometimes,
we take the spleen‐ic route.

14:54.645 --> 14:56.647
So...

14:59.900 --> 15:02.861
