15:15.791 --> 15:17.876
and seeing Beyoncé!

15:17.876 --> 15:19.503
‐ Oh...

15:20.045 --> 15:22.130
‐ I can't believe I'm getting engaged!

15:28.554 --> 15:30.597
‐ Look at that!
