15:34.142 --> 15:37.396
‐ I love you so much.
‐ I love you more.

15:37.396 --> 15:40.858
‐ And I love hilarious phone mishaps.

15:42.067 --> 15:45.237
We swapped in the Uber.
Mazel tov, by the way.

15:45.696 --> 15:48.323
‐ Uh, here. It's dead,
which feels very on brand for you.

15:48.323 --> 15:49.825
Um, I'm sorry.

15:50.325 --> 15:51.368
‐ Mm!

15:52.995 --> 15:54.705
‐ Oh my god.
‐ What?

15:54.705 --> 15:57.541
‐ There were so many men
urinating in there at once.

15:57.541 --> 15:59.543
