in this hellscape.

16:13.515 --> 16:16.226
‐ This hellscape is my daily life,

16:16.226 --> 16:17.644
you prissy royal bitch.

16:17.644 --> 16:19.146
‐ Hey...

16:21.982 --> 16:23.066
‐ Mm!

16:23.066 --> 16:25.319
‐ Mm?
