23:18.106 --> 23:20.234
‐ Whoo!
‐ Now, we're talking!

23:20.234 --> 23:22.903
Listen, what are we gonna do for dinner?
Because it's late...

23:25.364 --> 23:27.658
‐ Thanks for having us
